# JavaFX Registration System (Java + MySQL)

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is a **JavaFX-based Registration System** where users can register through a graphical interface and their details are stored  in a **MySQL database** using **JDBC**.

---

## ğŸ¯ Why This Project?

This mini project was built to:

* Strengthen **Java backend fundamentals**
* Learn **database connectivity using JDBC**
* Understand **real-world data flow** from UI â†’ backend â†’ database
* Practice **project structuring using Maven**

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack & Tools Used

| Technology          | Purpose                                |
| ------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| **Java**            | Core programming language              |
| **JavaFX**          | GUI development                        |
| **FXML**            | UI layout separation from logic        |
| **CSS**             | Styling the JavaFX UI                  |
| **MySQL**           | Persistent data storage                |
| **JDBC**            | Connecting Java application with MySQL |
| **Maven**           | Dependency management & project build  |
| **Properties File** | Externalized database configuration    |

