* REST-based backend 

---

## ğŸ“Œ Conclusion
This project demonstrates how a JavaFX desktop application can interact with a MySQL database using JDBC to handle real-world user registration scenarios.
 By building this system,  I gained practical experience in GUI development,
  backend logic, and database connectivity, along with a better understanding of application workflow 
 and data consistency.
